data.description: Welcome to this stunning brick home, offering a luxurious and spacious living experience. Built in 2020, this home boasts impeccable craftsmanship and modern finishes throughout. Upon entering, you will be greeted by a grand foyer that leads you to the main living area. The family room is the heart of the home, featuring a cozy fireplace and large windows that fill the space with natural light. The adjacent kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with stone counters, a stylish kitchen island, and top-of-the-line appliances. It is perfect for hosting gatherings and preparing delicious meals for your loved ones. This home offers a total of 5 bedrooms, providing ample space for a growing family or accommodating guests. The master bedroom is a true retreat, with a sitting room that offers a peaceful sanctuary to relax and unwind. With its spacious layout, modern features, and desirable community amenities, this home is truly a gem. Come and experience the epitome of luxury living in this remarkable residence. Qualifies for 100% financing through PATH home loan!
